\rm\ mod\ 13\!:\, \ \begin{eqnarray}1\,\equiv&& -12\\ 10\,\equiv&& -3\end{eqnarray}\,\ \Rightarrow\,\ \dfrac{1}{10}\,\equiv\, \dfrac{-12}{-3}\,\equiv\, 4,\ 
